Title: Marathon Gear Essentials
Body HTML:
Marathon Preparation Essentials

While one can argue that all you need for a marathon are proper shoes, adding in a few pieces of gear can improve your overall marathon experience. Here is a quick list of some items that you can add to your marathon gear list:

  • Running Shoes
  • Hydration Pack or Vest
  • Performance Running Shirt
  • Running Bottoms (Shorts, tights, pants)
  • Running Sunglasses
  • Hydration Belt

These are some of the items that can make help you be prepared for your upcoming marathon. Have fun, perform, and good luck in your race!

Body HTML:
Beachwear & Accessories

Nathan beachwear features our patented quick-drying and high-performance technology to keep you cool and comfortable. Whether you are beach running, playing volleyball or relaxing on the sand by the water – Nathan has you covered.

Post Workout Apparel

No matter the activity, throw these on as you leave the gym, finish your run, or head back from the trails.

From cozy hoodies to our ultra-soft joggers, we’ve put together the best-in-class post workout gear to help you recover and get going. Perfect for warm-up, cool down, or for everyday lounging and everything in between.


Shop Post-Workout Apparel & Accessories: Men’s Hoodies  | Women’s Hoodies | Women’s Tank Tops | Men’s Tank Tops | Women’s Joggers | Men’s Joggers | Women’s Shorts | Men’s Shorts ","hiddenProducts":[],"collectionBanner":[]}
